title: Lady Antebellum - Wheels Up Tour - 2015 - 1080p AC3
description:
Lady Antebellum - Wheels Up Tour - 2015

The Lady Antebellum "Wheels Up" world-wide tour started in Oslo, Norway on Feb 28, 2015. It then worked its way through Sweden, Scotland, Ireland, England, Australia, Canada and the USA. They performed at 65 separate venues. The tour concluded in Las Vegas on Oct 3, 2015.

This particular concert was performed at the Verizon Wireless Amphitheatre in Irvine, California on June 27, 2015. The music and the stage presentation is awesome.

This video is a shortened version of the full concert, released early to promote the upcoming commercial CD, DVD and Bluray to be available on Nov 13, 2015. If you enjoy this music video then please purchase the commercial version.

Video: MPEG-4, AVC (H.264), 1080p, 13.8Mbps at 29.97fps
Audio: AC-3, 6-channel, Dolby 5.1, 384Kbps, 48KHz, 16-bits
Duration: 38 minutes
